&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Central Liverpool Primary Care Network&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Support Assistant Band 3 22.5 hours per week&lt;em&gt;(Job description attached)&lt;/em&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Central Liverpool Primary Care Network is looking to strengthen its Project Team to support delivery of its Network priorities.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;The Support Assistant will provide an efficient admin and diary management support role to the team and CLPCN overall. Experience of managing diaries, meetings and GPTeamNet would be an advantage.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;For further information please contact Lorraine.McDonagh@livgp@nhs.uk&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Closing Date: 10th November 2020&lt;br /&gt; Interview date: 18th November 2020&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;If you have not heard back within 4 weeks after closing date, please assume your application has been unsuccessful.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt; &lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;We do not accept CV applications - you must apply via NHS Jobs. &lt;/p&gt;
